    {
      "id": "PopularPost267665",
      "post_content": "I'm gonna go with recent releases from M13: [Fervor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fervor), [Krenko's Command](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krenko's Command) and [Krenko, Mob Boss](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krenko, Mob Boss) all love this card. Why? Turn 6, you play this and swing with a flying 5/5, after playing Krenko. Turn 7, you tap Krenko for more tokens, and use Moonveil Dragon's ability to boost all of the tokens up by 5+ power. Then you have a swarm of haste Goblin tokens attacking, each with 6-8 power, depending on your mana. Either way, unless your opponent has his own token army, or an amazing god-draw of mass removal, you probably win. No, most likely you do win. This just makes red tokens amazing.",
      "posted_by": "AeternusEclipse",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost267665\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_post\">I'm gonna go with recent releases from M13: <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fervor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fervor\">Fervor</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Krenko's Command\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krenko's Command\">Krenko's Command</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Krenko, Mob Boss\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Krenko, Mob Boss\">Krenko, Mob Boss</a> all love this card. Why? Turn 6, you play this and swing with a flying 5/5, after playing Krenko. Turn 7, you tap Krenko for more tokens, and use Moonveil Dragon's ability to boost all of the tokens up by 5+ power. Then you have a swarm of haste Goblin tokens attacking, each with 6-8 power, depending on your mana. Either way, unless your opponent has his own token army, or an amazing god-draw of mass removal, you probably win. No, most likely you do win. This just makes red tokens amazing.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '267665'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy80195\">AeternusEclipse</span>\r\n                                (9/11/2012 2:09:31 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"